{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775670/extras/TitleHeader.gif?t=1730743289\" />Toadally Dreadful is a Throwback 90's mascot horror. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Summer Science Camp is going to be fun...Not! Hey, but like for real... where are the other campers? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lake Oakwood... more like Lake Croakwood\u2026 Let\u2019s hope we can escape from the freaky frog frights or this campout will be TOADALLY DREADFUL!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775670/extras/Lakeside-Lamp.gif?t=1730743289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Something at Lake Oakwood has caused the other campers to go missing. Now you gotta solve the secrets of the campground, the lake and surrounding forest, an environment filled with radical mysteries, bodacious puzzles, and tubular terrors. Build makeshift defenses like s\u2019mores snares, camera traps, and firefly decoys against the sinister presence that lurks within the trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775670/extras/Why-so-Quiet.gif?t=1730743289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect the pieces of the story to what is really happening, and make sure to be back in your bunk before curfew! Three days till Mom comes to pick you up. Can you go that long without croaking?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775670/extras/Lamp.gif?t=1730743289\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730743289","background_r